<HEAD>URGENT</HEAD>
<HEAD>NEW YORK: officials said.</HEAD>
<TEXT>
   The plane, USAir Flight 5050, a Boeing 737-400, went down on
takeoff from LaGuardia, bound for Charlotte, N.C., said Susan Young,
a USAir spokewoman in Pittsburgh.
   ``On takeoff it went off the end of the runway and it is now
partially submerged in the water,'' she said.
   Young had no information about the number of people aboard or
possible injuries.
