<HEAD>Shevardnadze Gives Bush Mosaic of Capital Sites</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-US-Soviet, Bjt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Soviet Foreign Minister Eduard Shevardnadze on
Thursday gave President Bush an unusual gift _ a mosaic on copper of
the capital's most famous sights, including the White House,
Washington Monument and Lincoln Memorial.
   Bush brought the Soviet visitor into his private study in the
